data.description: Immaculate 3 bedroom ranch, original owners. New roof and hot water tank with new plumbing and newer washtubs. Spacious kitchen comes complete with new counter tops and Samsung stainless steel refrigerator, stove and microwave, Stainless steel Bosch dishwasher.  Electrolux washer and dryer with pedestals in the laundry room. Plenty of storage space.   Situated on a quiet cul-de sac street.  Easy access to the city of Pittsburgh and I-376 the Parkway. Easy access to shopping and the busway.   Large private covered patio with awnings, privacy fence and a shed. Large integral garage.
